<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克非常害怕，他在等食人魔离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打开了烤箱门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他准备跳出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是食人魔的妻子阻止了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！”她小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在还不安全，你再等等！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我丈夫一般吃了早饭后会睡一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克叹了口气，关上了烤箱门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，食人魔回来了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克躲在烤箱里往外看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔开始吃他的巨大的煎饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！真好吃！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>盘子很快就空了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻，吃得真快！”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老婆！”食人魔大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再给我做一些煎饼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，亲爱的！”他的妻子回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃……”杰克心想，“他吃得这么多，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我什么时候才能出去……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克一直等啊等，食人魔一直吃呀吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，食人魔吃完站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“终于吃完了！”杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在他要去睡觉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是食人魔没有去睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走向一个大箱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在做什么？”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔打开了箱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出来两个袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“箱子里全是金子和宝物！”杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“里面肯定也有我们的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
